{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"102f3bd1fa","title":"“我院的党委是一团糟，腐化了”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f9c1cf8b07","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"102f3bd1fa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"229f6e017a","name":"龚汝劼"},{"id":"25d93d6f1a","name":"于淑文"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"edc00df2f2","name":"刘德昭"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0a59f3bee6","type":"title","text":"“我院的党委是一团糟，腐化了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"26ccb5ca28","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院于淑文刘德昭龚汝劼","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"93c97798a3","type":"appellation","text":"于淑文说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"2ea7171f78","type":"appellation","text":"“我院的党委是一团糟，腐化了。我院由于温昌芸事件的揭发，可以看出是到处黑暗，见不到光明，我真象生活在魔鬼峡谷中。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"ede8533c93","type":"appellation","text":"刘德昭说:","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"e42064f434","type":"appellation","text":"“同意‘私产党’和‘集体分肥’的论调，反右派本身就是一种‘私’的表现。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"f1ef67fe85","type":"appellation","text":"龚汝劼说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"6a56c57e0d","type":"appellation","text":"“当党委变质后，整风不能解决怎么办？”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"b3056f4603","type":"appellation","text":"“中国革命是伟大的，领导中国进行革命，但为什么地院的党组织没有达到这种要求，未达标准？”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"5c8083e3d5","type":"appellation","text":"“党要象党章上规定那样可以代表人民利益，但实际上做不到。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"7c9e2f2e25","type":"appellation","text":"“老干部对任何事只会享乐，不愿吃苦，对自己考虑很多，如陈子谷。物探楼不好，学生伙食不好，但他胖了。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"6a255700f1","type":"appellation","text":"“每一个党员不能百分之百的掌握马列主义，党是否保证他不发生变质，不能保证则不能对党有无条件信任。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"},{"id":"a7c058bfad","type":"appellation","text":"“无条件信任是指在一定时间内不发生变质而已，否则马万钧的推理二次革命是合理的，有二次革命的话，也是无产阶级革命”。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa"}],"page":{"id":"69a9525199","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"102f3bd1fa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}